{"type":"article_comment","id":458381,"parentType":"article","parentId":22174,"uid":53857,"contents":"第二期概览：<br>\n<br>\n<b>本期主题：信息自由</b><br>\n<br>\n<b>主编：PC</b><br>\n<br>\n信息就是力量。在互联网的世界里，信息是思想的火药，所以审查者们筑起防火墙来熄灭点燃的炸药。<br>\n<br>\n他们害怕信息的自由流通，<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20150904-mainland-greatfirewall/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">对外建墙</a>，<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20180327-notes-china-censorship/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">对内审查</a>，严重损害了人们自由获取信息的权利。因为他们害怕真相，连备份公开信息都成为罪行，可见他们是多么地脆弱，一点真相的影子都让他们颤抖。<br>\n<br>\n信息渴望自由。掌握真相的权利将回到人们手中，而墙最后的结局是无一例外地被推翻。<br>\n<br>\n<b><a href=\"https://2049post.wordpress.com/category/%e5%88%8a%e7%89%a9%e7%89%88%e5%9d%97/%e7%ab%af%e7%82%b9%e6%98%9f%e4%b9%8b%e5%a3%b0/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">端点星之声</a></b><br>\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://2049post.wordpress.com/2020/08/01/v2voice1/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">端点星案：无法抹杀的记忆</a></li></ul><br>\n<br>\n<b><a href=\"https://2049post.wordpress.com/category/%e5%88%8a%e7%89%a9%e7%89%88%e5%9d%97/%e6%96%87%e8%89%ba%e6%9d%82%e8%b0%88/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">文艺杂谈</a></b><br>\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://2049post.wordpress.com/2020/08/01/v2poet2/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">诗歌：小二，早点回家</a></li><li><a href=\"https://2049post.wordpress.com/2020/08/01/v2poet1/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">诗歌：我们和他们</a></li><li><a href=\"https://2049post.wordpress.com/2020/08/01/v2art1/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">艺术与星辰：《Saturn食子》</a></li><li><a href=\"https://2049post.wordpress.com/2020/08/01/v2art2/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">北京狐狸的浮世绘：“顶替上学”系列</a></li><li><a href=\"https://2049post.wordpress.com/2020/08/01/v2book1/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">读书推荐：爱德华·斯诺登 – 永久记录</a></li><li><a href=\"https://2049post.wordpress.com